《'''-{zh:索尔之子;zh-hans:索尔之子;zh-hant:索爾之子;zh-hk:天堂無門;zh-mo:天堂無門;zh-tw:索爾之子;}-'''》（{{lang-hu|''Saul fia''}}）是一部於2015年上映的[[匈牙利|匈牙利]][[劇情片|劇情片]]，为[[拉斯洛·奈迈施|拉斯洛·奈迈施]]执导的首部电影长片。入选[[第68届戛纳电影节|第68届戛纳电影节]]主竞赛片<ref name="2015Cannes">{{cite web |url=http://www.festival-cannes.com/en/article/61306.html |title=2015 Official Selection |accessdate=16 April 2015 |work=Cannes |archive-date=2015-04-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150418084150/http://www.festival-cannes.com/en/article/61306.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.festival-cannes.fr/en/article/61347.html|title=Screenings Guide|work=Festival de Cannes|date=6 May 2015|accessdate=8 May 2015|archive-date=2015-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518080922/http://www.festival-cannes.fr/en/article/61347.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>并赢得评审团大奖<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://ent.163.com/15/0525/02/AQE64KOF00034VCU.html |title=拉斯洛·奈迈施凭《索尔之子》获本届评审团大奖 |access-date=2015-05-27 |archive-date=2017-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201043000/http://ent.163.com/15/0525/02/AQE64KOF00034VCU.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，以及[[第73届金球奖|第73届金球奖]]最佳外语片<ref name="Golden Globe Award">{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/lists/golden-globes-winners-2016-list-853010|title=Golden Globes: The Complete Winners List|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=11 January 2016|accessdate=11 January 2016|archive-date=2016-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160406153242/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/lists/golden-globes-winners-2016-list-853010|dead-url=no}}</ref>和[[第88屆奧斯卡金像獎|第88屆奧斯卡金像獎]]最佳外語片<ref name="WinnerHWR">{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/2016-oscars-best-foreign-language-869714 |title=Oscars: Hungary Wins Its First Foreign-Language Honor Since Fall of Communism |work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |last=Szalai |first=Georg |date=28 February 2016 |accessdate=29 February 2016 |archive-date=2016-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309124335/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/2016-oscars-best-foreign-language-869714 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，成為首部獲得[[金球獎最佳外語片|金球獎最佳外語片]]的匈牙利電影<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/golden-globes-hungary-celebrates-first-854446|title=Golden Globes: Hungary Celebrates First-Ever Win for 'Son of Saul'|author=Nick Holdsworth|date=11 January 2016|accessdate=16 January 2016|work=The Hollywood Reporter|archive-date=2021-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417204838/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/golden-globes-hungary-celebrates-first-854446|dead-url=no}}</ref>，以及继1981年的《[[千面恶魔梅菲斯托|千面恶魔梅菲斯托]]》之后第二部获得[[奥斯卡最佳外语片|奥斯卡最佳外语片]]的匈牙利电影。

== 剧情 ==
1944年10月，匈牙利人索尔是[[奥斯维辛集中营|奥斯维辛集中营]]里负责处理死者的囚犯分遣队成员，在一次在焚尸炉处理尸体时，他发现了一名猶太男孩的尸体。索尔决定偷偷带走尸体，给他举行一个正式的犹太教[[葬礼|葬礼]]。经过努力索尔找到了一个犹太教士，想让教士帮孩子举行犹太葬礼......

